Hobbies

In addition to my professional pursuits, I am an individual with a deep passion for reading, writing, cinema, and sport, which collectively enrich my life by fostering knowledge acquisition, creativity, effective communication, critical thinking, and a well-rounded, balanced approach to personal and professional development.
